---
---

<section class="band-amber">
  <div class="section taproom-grid" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.2fr 1fr;gap:56px;align-items:center;">
    <div>
      <span class="kicker reveal" style="color:var(--ink-2);">The Taproom · 1051 Main Street, Hampton</span>
      <h2 class="display reveal d1" style="font-size:clamp(40px,5.2vw,72px);margin:14px 0 20px;color:var(--ink);line-height:0.92;">Pull Up<br />A Stool</h2>
      <p class="reveal d1" style="font-size:18px;line-height:1.65;color:var(--ink-2);max-width:480px;">Twelve taps poured fresh, live music on the weekends, and a laid-back patio on the river. Kids and families are always welcome — board games, colouring, and non-alcoholic options on hand. Whether you're stopping in or staying all night, there's always something new on tap.</p>
      <div class="reveal d2" style="margin-top:30px;display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/visit" style="border-color:var(--ink);color:var(--ink);">Hours &amp; Directions</a>
        <a class="btn" href="#events" style="background:var(--ink);color:var(--cream);">What's On →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="reveal d1" style="display:grid;grid-template-rows:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;height:100%;">
      <img class="photo" src="/assets/photos/beer-flight-table.png" alt="A flight of Gridiron beers on a wooden table" style="aspect-ratio:16/9;object-position:center;" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
      <img class="photo" src="/assets/photos/chalkboard-taps.png" alt="Gridiron chalkboard tap list and taps" style="aspect-ratio:16/9;object-position:center top;" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
